"replyTime":"2020-02-24T16:06:08.000Z","msg":"根本話阿古路勁d的人，都未睇過..."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T16:16:39.000Z","msg":"未睇過乜野"},{"pid":"e309e107a508380c1eb9866fee13a904abd5d56b","tid":1895634,"uid":209773,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T16:17:47.000Z","msg":"真係好傷心，比我喺度叫下春，希望咁多位唔好覺得我矯情<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小弟本身都係追開屁馬同so9（差d做咗利狗），同時都好欣賞美斯球技，兩年間兩位轉曬去巴，我就開始跟進巴塞波。但係4年前三冠王我都無太大感覺，因為我嗰陣使確實只係中意一堆球星嘅巴塞，唔係真係中意巴塞。<br />\n兩年前因為大病住撚左半年院，巴塞同我渡過咗無數個夜晚，我就確確實實認定咗自己係巴塞迷，開始成屋巴塞poster，叫女朋友生日禮物唔使諗直接送波衫。<br />\n入到大學之後時間多咗，基本上有巴塞嘅不論咩賽事我都會睇，甚至癲到叫埋女朋友一齊去學西班牙文，諗住遲啲就移民去巴塞，住喺魯營隔離，平日放工就踢拖落街睇波。<br />\n呢兩年，有見到我開post嘅人都知，基本上朝早六七點仲喺波台鳩up，贏波就去撚鳩人，輸波就扮其他球迷廢up，為咗睇波，連身體都可以拎去捱。<br />\n到今日，我真係開始反思下咁樣做係咪真係值得，我做咗真疤四年，三年八強出局，兩年柒到甩轆，而令我中意巴塞嘅球員一個一個咁離開，馬斯沙維尼馬小白，蘇狗碧基影帝艾巴，到美斯走嘅時候，我怕我真係會頂唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係好想見到希望，好想見到新嘅氣象，變返以前地上最強嘅氣勢，好想享受下做真疤奪歐冠嘅滋味，求下你華狗你不如走啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1c5ce9c831ef108719a84c28efa23730101d0f0","tid":1895634,"uid":36040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b4a735d52fe9f255766798c02a8e0b6d26dd1bc","tid":1895634,"uid":84834,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a2bcc8cd3f07912fa7106c96843be7b368d79704","tid":1895634,"uid":36040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T16:10:25.000Z","msg":"拎過世界杯未?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T16:11:35.000Z","msg":"18歲就拎青年軍世界杯啦，清坐咗幾耐？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T16:19:58.000Z","msg":"青年軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97072b6c4699091de79775b4c63d705f0880cae8","tid":1895634,"uid":61905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T16:20:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1059195/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1059195/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=27558018&amp;extra=&amp;page=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.discuss.com.hk%2Fviewthread.php%3Ftid%3D27558018%26extra%3D%26page%3D21&d=MxNsT%2FmsUjaXWzHBtsAqwYCLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=927ef97d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=27558018&amp;extra=&amp;page=21</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35d23ffbfd9b89bec5a5a8394d27d076f8b4fbf3","tid":1895634,"uid":84834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0462fffdc68a1bb01de42854d196cd8705609f1f","tid":1895634,"uid":45301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9376a8f50fba42bc8c03f63e21fe04c93965baca","tid":1895634,"uid":84834,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b59d111b32739656ccf43b98b21aae90fe63e229","tid":1895634,"uid":119729,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T16:05:18.000Z","msg":"阿古路係英超勁足咁多年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T16:06:08.000Z","msg":"根本話阿古路勁d的人，都未睇過..."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T16:16:39.000Z","msg":"未睇過乜野"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T16:21:24.000Z","msg":"未睇過美斯全盛嗰陣有幾恐怖囉，你新會然？"},{"pid":"438757113a624f257a4931d9c3fce40c2015bb30","tid":1895634,"uid":141543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T16:22:59.000Z","msg":"花迷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7740e4adc731668996e9372cfa3657452ad5f963","tid":1895634,"uid":116896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T16:44:40.000Z","msg":"咁講真<br />\n賤種特最多似賤種朗咁都係偽球王"},{"pid":"308a789e299b96b648ae37aec5717fbb52466dd5","tid":1895634,"uid":69568,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T16:52:35.000Z","msg":"講埋呢次<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.makeagif.com/media/5-03-2019/vTE8dv.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.makeagif.com%2Fmedia%2F5-03-2019%2FvTE8dv.gif&h=91050308&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n就好似第二球咁<br />\n一個美斯帶波引左4個防守球員mark佢<br />\n樓下蘇狗完全空哂<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.makeagif.com/media/5-03-2019/21TqsL.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.makeagif.com%2Fmedia%2F5-03-2019%2F21TqsL.gif&h=8dbbb441&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲有呢球反擊<br />\n個波一傳左去美斯到<br />\n就全部人撲埋去<br />\n完全冇人理碧基 丹比利<br />\n如果唔係炒粉 咁就已經4比0<br />\n<br />\n睇咁耐波<br />\n除左巴西朗拿度top fit個幾年<br />\n真係未見過防守個邊會咁驚一個球員<br />\n<br />\n呢個已經係級數上的分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日日係到爭論邊個入600球先<br />\n邊個有咩冠軍<br />\n邊個幾多球金球<br />\n<br />\n根本完全唔重要<br />\n睜大啲隻眼睇下波<br />\n用個腦諗下<br />\n其實真係會睇到個分別係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利伸：無意貶低其他球員"}]}